Warm <HI>Bath,</HI> as productive of an inflammatory heat, which
occa&s;ions a dangerous di&s;ten&s;ion of the ve&s;&s;els. But how
&s;hall we reconcile this opinion with that of the accurate,
the experienced <HI>Hoffman,</HI> who pronounces the u&s;e of the
