of the <HI>Vial</HI> in which it was contained&mdash;What is effected
by Art, is &s;ometimes performed by Nature, in the bowels
of the earth.&mdash;The effects of &s;ubterraneous fire are mani|fe&s;t
in the eruptions of every <HI>V$lcano;</HI> in <HI>Earthquakes,
Hurricanes, Mineral Damps,</HI> and <HI>Exhalations,</HI> term$d by
the ancients, <HI>Mephi$$s:</HI> but, in nothing are they more
