now claim my ob&s;ervation.</P>
<P>There is in the $span$ Waters, for the mo&s;t
$span$ which is not ea&s;ily re|tained
when they $span$ from the Spring head; and
$span$ to the nerves, as
$span$ in the very in&s;tant of drinking.
<PB N="29" REF="31">
Though this very &s;ubtile &s;pirit is, in part, di&s;&s;ipated by the
