Highne&s;s the Prince of <HI>Wales,</HI> by who&s;e command they
were &s;ent to Mr. <HI>Na&s;h,</HI> with a de&s;ire that he would lay
them before the corporation, in his name&mdash;Yet, notwith|&s;tanding
